item.title: 【Singles (lossless)】FLAC - Jenni Rivera - Aparentemente Bien (2019) | Qobuz Hi-Res 24bit / 44.1kHz
item.description:
Aparentemente Bien is a song performed by American-Mexican singer, Jenni Rivera. It was released posthumously as a single by Rivera's estate on her fiftieth birthday, July 2, 2019, through Sony Music Latin. The single included Latin pop and mariachi versions of the song. The song would later be included in the posthumous album Misión Cumplida (2023), as the lead single. The song was written by "Despacito" co-writers Alejandro Lerner and Erika Ender, while production was done by Juan and Rosie Rivera.
